API Client to gather information about Github Users/Orgs/Repos

What:
	Connect to Github to retrieve information from:
		Users
		Organizations
		Repos

	From each category filter types of information such as:
		User:
			id:integer
			username:string
			repos:string
			email:string
			location:string

		Orgnizations:
			members:string
			location:string

		Repos:
			owner: User
			id:integer
			name:string
			language:string
			commits:integer
How:
	Connecting to Github API,
	Retrieve information (JSON) via AJAX with jQuery
